If you are in debian or ubuntu system, run this command
to install all required packages:

    sudo apt-get install gir1.2-keybinder-3.0 python-xlib python-notify2


and then, to init azulejo you can run:

    python run.py


or to install:

    sudo apt-get install gir1.2-keybinder-3.0 python-xlib
    sudo python setup.py install

and then, from any path you can run:

    azulejo
